LanguageData.JRWStyracosaurusReconstruct.label: Styracosaurus
LanguageData.JRWStyracosaurusReconstruct.description:
-- > INGEN INTERNAL CASE FILE #039902-1913 [STYRACOSAURUS ALBERTENSIS] CODENAME: STYRAX >230
A ceratopsian well known for the multitude of spikes decorating its head. Smaller than most ceratopsians, they often use their lesser stature for speed rather than strength.
